This is the source code for my personal portfolio website,
this website uses a template generator I wrote to pre-load
all my user repo data from the github api. You can see
this in action looking in the source/update.sh script 
which pulls the latest json data from github and uses the
generator to load the data to the website, this loaded 
page is then written to index.html at the root of the 
project and will then of course be displayed on the main
page. This process allows for the website to be static
with periodically dynamic data. 

If you're interested in using a similar approach to 
preload your websites data then go check out my repo for
my template-generator:

https://github.com/x3hy/plate

